A vibrant Studio Ghibli style illustration of a festive Chinese New Year celebration scene in Singapore, featuring a family gathering around a round table filled with traditional reunion dinner dishes including whole fish, dumplings, and tangerines. Red paper lanterns hang overhead casting warm golden light, while through an open window fireworks bloom across a twilight sky. A playful lion dance costume lies draped over a chair in the corner. The scene radiates warmth, prosperity, and joyful anticipation, with rich crimson and gold tones dominating the palette. Soft, painterly brushstrokes give the image a dreamy, nostalgic quality with detailed textures on the lacquered furniture and silk decorations.
